comments.body:
I slightly prefer to have the full syntax at the syntax section without having a second layer of sub-syntax at the parameters section. 
@srowen Do you have a preference?
I took a look of SHOW TABLE, ALTER TABLE, TRUNCATE TABLE, the syntax partition_spec is not  consistent among them, either. For the most common parameters, such as partition_spec, table_name, database_name, etc. we need to have an agreed syntax, and then use the same syntax for all the commands. I guess I will need to spend some time to take care of the consistency.
